Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.60,0:01:42.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要去斯卡布罗集市吗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.85,0:01:49.58,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欧芹 鼠尾草 迷迭香和百里香
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.99,0:01:56.59,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请代我向住在那里的一个人问好…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.05,0:01:58.32,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来是奏人君啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.57,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊 唯小姐
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.46,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夜色真美啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.11,0:02:09.03,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为什么要坐在那种地方呢
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.90,0:02:10.68,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很危险的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.31,0:02:12.68,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没事的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.90,0:02:15.12,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 真的很危险啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.07,0:02:21.96,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你脸上又是害怕又是焦躁的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.05,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的是 非常可爱
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.67,0:02:30.27,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其实我最讨厌你那种表情了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.03,0:02:34.35,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想着 为什么你会怕我
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.65,0:02:36.38,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这会让我很不安
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.17,0:02:38.87,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现…现在不是的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.44,0:02:42.20,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为奏人君你好像快掉下去了 我才会害怕…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.07,0:02:47.10,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}反正你是不会知道
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.69,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自己有多自以为是吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.78,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}愚蠢至极
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.54,0:02:59.59,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蠢得让人发笑 这点也让人觉得可爱
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.78,0:03:03.00,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不可以担心你吗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.27,0:03:05.52,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对我来说那是毫无用处的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.17,0:03:08.93,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.22,0:03:13.04,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你那么想要我从这儿下来吗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.04,0:03:17.72,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 吻我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.99,0:03:22.70,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你愿意吻我的话 我下来也无妨
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.16,0:03:27.51,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你说不要的话
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.48,0:03:32.00,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就请你不要管我 赶紧消失吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.22,0:03:33.79,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.06,0:03:42.80,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.28,0:03:46.15,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你居然当真了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.34,0:03:52.24,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果真是个无可救药的笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.54,0:03:55.97,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我下来就是了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.24,0:03:57.76,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊 真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.86,0:03:58.32,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.14,0:04:01.81,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏 奏人君
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.09,0:04:06.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 再见了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.01,0:04:07.52,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.07,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏人君
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.48,0:04:22.32,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你没事吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.18,0:04:25.54,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏人君 奏人君
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.08,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你好烦啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.76,0:04:31.16,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过是从二楼掉下来
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.54,0:04:34.68,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你觉得我会有什么事吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.09,0:04:35.63,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.01,0:04:39.96,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果这样就能死的话倒是轻松不少
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.23,0:04:43.85,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想死…吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.69,0:04:48.40,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}话虽如此 不过不是现在
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.62,0:04:56.62,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对了 我有个很中意的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.98,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天就破例带唯小姐过去
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.04,0:05:09.85,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这些是
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.50,0:05:12.42,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如你所见 是蜡像
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.18,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还是第一次看见
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.21,0:05:19.10,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}泰迪一来这里心情就会变得很好
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.10,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对吧 泰迪
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.43,0:05:26.73,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看起来不怎么开心啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.68,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我总觉得蜡像有点恐怖
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.98,0:05:34.17,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}像泰迪那么可爱的倒还好
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.79,0:05:38.90,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我当然知道泰迪是最可爱的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.72,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过 从已经「失去灵魂」
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.85,0:05:46.18,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这层意思上看 泰迪也是一样的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.53,0:05:48.40,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「失去灵魂」？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.27,0:05:55.41,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}若你变成{\rTEXT-CN-RED\blur2}无法言语的尸体{\r\blur2} 会何等美丽呢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.97,0:05:56.35,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.73,0:06:01.11,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想不想变成人偶 现在 就在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.28,0:06:02.66,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏 奏人君
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.93,0:06:04.93,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会精心装扮你
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.25,0:06:08.09,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 你在说什么
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.99,0:06:13.21,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}泰迪也一定会因为有了新伙伴而高兴的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.02,0:06:18.16,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对唯小姐而言 也没有什么损失吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.83,0:06:19.91,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.13,0:06:25.92,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我绝对不想…成为人偶
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.44,0:06:37.04,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为什么要那么害怕呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.47,0:06:40.80,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过 真是不错的表情啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.64,0:06:42.37,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.80,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真不错啊 这个表情
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.15,0:06:48.10,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是漂亮极了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.02,0:06:54.19,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因恐惧而扭曲的表情 为什么会这么诱人呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.00,0:06:56.62,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.49,0:07:00.44,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏人君 我求求你
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.57,0:07:01.44,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快住手
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.55,0:07:07.07,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让我把你这张烦人的嘴完美地缝合起来吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.12,0:07:07.53,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.26,0:07:11.21,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会在你的眼睛里镶入玻璃珠
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.88,0:07:13.67,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么颜色好呢
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.34,0:07:17.83,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因鲜血尽失而变得晶莹通透的肌肤
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.27,0:07:22.92,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会变得像陶瓷一样洁白光滑吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.50,0:07:35.63,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会好好喝干你的血的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.39,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请不用担心
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.88,0:07:43.48,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你一定会比任何新娘都美丽
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.61,0:07:48.40,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这 这些蜡像 难道是…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.35,0:07:50.65,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没错
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.76,0:07:54.11,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她们就是那些{\rTEXT-CN-RED\blur2}祭品新娘
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.82,0:08:00.20,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}马上就会让你觉得舒服的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.28,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好难…受
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.10,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏人
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.43,0:08:16.73,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怜司叫你
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.48,0:08:20.54,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好麻烦啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.27,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绫人君
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.25,0:08:28.63,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别误会
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.96,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天没什么兴致
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.48,0:08:41.45,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好累
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.11,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昴君
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.93,0:09:02.98,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 要是继续待在这里的话 必死无疑
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.66,0:09:07.66,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是…我也没办法…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.24,0:09:13.21,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在的话…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.94,0:09:17.43,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.30,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果是现在的话…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.89,0:09:47.30,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然 我还是想知道真相
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.90,0:09:55.79,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昴君
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.55,0:10:01.93,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你没有逃走吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.23,0:10:05.83,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这种机会可是很难得的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.94,0:10:07.64,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.40,0:10:12.08,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你知道关于我父亲的事 就请告诉我
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.43,0:10:17.68,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们说我是教会献出的祭品
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.11,0:10:19.68,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我什么都不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.80,0:10:32.28,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.42,0:10:40.05,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果用这把银制匕首刺进我们吸血鬼的胸口
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.94,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就能置我们于死地
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.08,0:10:44.54,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶 为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.82,0:10:55.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请拿着它
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.82,0:10:58.42,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请寸不离身地拿好它
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.12,0:11:01.42,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}呐 快杀了他 杀了他啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.15,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要我杀死谁啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.23,0:11:06.61,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 你究竟是在对谁说话
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.53,0:11:09.24,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在向谁求助啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.10,TEXT-CN(UP),,0,0,0,,{\blur2}求求你快杀了他
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.75,0:11:06.96,TEXT-CN(UP),,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放我走吧 求求你 放我走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.72,0:11:12.92,TEXT-CN(UP),,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果做不到的话 你一定要用这把匕首刺穿我的心脏
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.13,0:11:12.46,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的眼中映着的 究竟是谁
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.92,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是个温柔的孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.46,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 我会杀死你的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.33,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是你的愿望吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.44,0:11:25.44,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一定会帮你实现它的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.93,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小贱人 我都等得不耐烦了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.45,0:11:34.26,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}礼人君
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.72,0:11:36.91,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.91,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}露出那副表情
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.10,0:11:41.89,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出去
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.54,0:11:47.33,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是认真的吗 小贱人
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.92,0:11:53.60,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昴君的匕首啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.69,0:12:00.20,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要做什么
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.10,0:12:05.94,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真荣幸啊 没想到你爱我那么深
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.75,0:12:07.21,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.94,0:12:13.40,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对于吸血鬼而言 杀死对方便是至高的爱的告白
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.51,0:12:20.74,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是为那些可谓拥有永恒生命的人们所落下的帷幕
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.79,0:12:23.50,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}礼…礼人君？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.77,0:12:26.15,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你可能不明白吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.44,0:12:29.53,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那种爱越深恨越切的感觉
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.58,0:12:35.34,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们啊 归根结底是相似的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.26,0:12:40.62,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你炙热的鲜血散发着极致的香气 低声诉求着
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.62,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}礼人君 放开我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.65,0:12:46.90,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道你在渴求着我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.14,0:12:50.06,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在说什么啊 请你放开我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.55,0:12:54.28,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说吧 喊出来吧 说你想要我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.31,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神并不存在
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.82,0:12:59.77,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你也不需要遵守规则
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.50,0:13:05.34,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}压抑隐藏自己的欲望生活 有意义吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.02,0:13:10.48,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有什么意义…我不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.62,0:13:16.22,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.60,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我相信
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.41,0:13:24.52,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不论发生多么痛苦的事 我都会相信
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.80,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为人类很脆弱
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.77,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以才要去相信
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.46,0:13:41.92,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}像小贱人这样的人 我还是第一次遇到呢
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.62,0:13:45.30,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之前只对你的血感兴趣
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.33,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过我改主意了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.10,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你所喜爱的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.67,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那双瞳中倒映的一切
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.40,0:14:40.35,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}除我以外的世界都沉入黑暗吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.35,0:14:44.90,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为 你需要注视的就只有我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.26,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让我来把你弄坏吧
